- About Arina East Residences

Seaside & MRT at your Doorstep

Welcome to Arina East Residences, where luxury meets tranquility in the picturesque neighborhood of Tanjong Rhu, Singapore. This exclusive residential development offers a unique blend of modern elegance and natural beauty, providing residents with a truly exceptional living experience.

Nature lovers and outdoor enthusiasts will appreciate the proximity of Arina East Residences to various recreational spots. The nearby East Coast Park offers an array of leisure activities, including cycling, jogging, water sports, and picnics by the beach. Residents can also explore the Kallang Riverside Park, perfect for scenic walks and unwinding amidst nature.

Future Katong Park MRT is located just less than 5 minutes walk from La Ville Condo. Connecting you to CBD, Orchard and upcoming Bayshore precinct.
